    <item>
      <title>Hardware Configuration</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/hardware/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/hardware/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;To create a reliable yet compact setup, I&amp;rsquo;ve carefully selected the following hardware components:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;GMKTec M5 Plus Mini PC:&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;gmktec-m5-plus-mini-pc&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#gmktec-m5-plus-mini-pc&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Processor&lt;/strong&gt;: AMD Ryzen 7 5825U (8C/16T, Up to 4.4GHz)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RAM&lt;/strong&gt;: 32GB DDR4&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Storage&lt;/strong&gt;: 1TB NVMe SSD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Graphics&lt;/strong&gt;: Integrated AMD Radeon (Supports 4K@60Hz Output)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Networking&lt;/strong&gt;:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WiFi 6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bluetooth 5.2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ethernet&lt;/strong&gt; (2.5 GbE)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operating System&lt;/strong&gt;: Proxmox VE 8.x (A baremetal hypervisor)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Cooling System&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;cooling-system&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#cooling-system&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An external cooling system like fan can help maintain temprature and keep the system stable under stress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

